## ūüď¶ COMPLETE SETUP SCRIPT

### `setup-all.sh`
```bash
#!/bin/bash
# COMPLETE TERMUX UI SETUP

echo "Downloading complete setup..."
curl -s https://raw.githubusercontent.com/your/repo/termux-ultimate-ui/install.sh | bash
curl -s https://raw.githubusercontent.com/your/repo/termux-ultimate-ui/themes/cyberpunk.properties > ~/.termux/cyberpunk.properties
curl -s https://raw.githubusercontent.com/your/repo/termux-ultimate-ui/themes/matrix.properties > ~/.termux/matrix.properties
curl -s https://raw.githubusercontent.com/your/repo/termux-ultimate-ui/animations/ascii-art.sh > ~/bin/hackerman
chmod +x ~/bin/*

echo "‚úÖ Complete! Restart Termux."
```

