## ūüéĮ QUICK REFERENCE

### Commands
| Command | Action |
|---------|--------|
| `matrix-rain` | Matrix animation |
| `fire-effect` | Fire animation |
| `hackerman` | ASCII art |
| `theme-switcher` | Change theme |
| `neofetch` | System info |
| `lsd` | Files with icons |
| `bat` | Syntax highlight |
| `fortune \| cowsay` | Random quote |

### Themes
| Theme | Look |
|-------|------|
| Cyberpunk | Neon pink/green |
| Matrix | Green terminal |
| Dracula | Purple dark |
| Nord | Arctic blue |
| Neon Night | Red/teal |

