## ūüöÄ INSTALLATION

### Option 1: One-Command
```bash
# Download and run
curl -s https://raw.githubusercontent.com/your/repo/termux-ultimate-ui/install.sh | bash
```

### Option 2: Manual
1. Download all files
2. Run `install.sh`
3. Choose theme with `theme-switcher`
4. Enjoy!

